This directory is for DLLs from hibiyasleep OverlayPlugin.

Download from: https://github.com/hibiyasleep/OverlayPlugin/releases

It needs to be installed and enabled in ACT, as per https://github.com/hibiyasleep/OverlayPlugin/blob/master/README-en.md

Copy the following DLLs into this directory:

  HTMLRenderer.dll
  Newtonsoft.Json.dll
  OverlayPlugin.dll
  OverlayPlugin.Core.dll
  OverlayPlugin.Common.dll
  Xilium.CefGlue.dll
